	[em 
		"Dizzy: The Ultimate Cartoon Adventure
	]em
	" is a platformer that was developed for early microcomputers such as the ZX Spectrum and the Commodore 64 and is the first game in the 
	[em 
		"Dizzy
	]em
	" series. Our hero Dizzy is off on a quest to stop the evil wizard Zaks from terrorizing the land of Katmandu by collecting a number of ingredients to concoct a potion that can defeat Zaks. However, it appears everything around Dizzy wants to kill him. With only a limited number of lives, Dizzy has to carefully maneuver around various hazards so he collect the necessary ingredients.
